            "answer_text": "NIOS provides the 5 years period to clear a class. After admission you will have 9 chances to appear in the examination. So you can appear in the upcoming examinayions (April/October exams). You need to appear for the failed subjects only.You can also apply for NIOS On Demand Examination, for which examinations are conducted throughout the year (except April,May, October, November).If you are finding any subject difficult then you also have the option to change the subject during thd admission period.Hope it Helps!!! ",
